Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.10,0:22:35.43,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}あぁ 朽ちていく世界ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:39.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}散りゆく運命ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.15,0:22:44.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}何を信じて生きればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:50.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}そう 君と出逢わなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:53.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}この胸を引き裂くような
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.96,0:22:59.63,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}痛みなんて知らなかったから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:04.33,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}空の彼方 鳴り響いた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.67,0:23:07.56,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}拙い鎮魂歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.67,0:23:07.56,ED,NTP,80,0,0,,{\be1\fs20}レクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.33,0:23:11.71,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}それでもまだ探している
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:14.80,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}不確かな現実から
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:14.80,ED,NTP,95,0,0,,{\be1\fs20}いま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.28,0:23:17.15,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}君のことを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:20.75,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}巡り逢えた歓びも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.89,0:23:24.48,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}消えていった温もりも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:28.73,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}ねぇ 全部覚えてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.00,0:23:31.77,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}愛してたから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:35.53,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}芽生えていく感情も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.73,0:23:39.30,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}胸に残る傷跡も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:43.45,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}ねぇ 全部抱えて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.78,0:23:50.38,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}この道を歩いて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.10,0:22:35.43,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}倘若世界將要腐朽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:39.00,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}如果註定難逃死滅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.15,0:22:44.00,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}此生究竟該相信什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:50.00,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}是的 如果不曾與你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:53.70,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我便不必體會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.96,0:22:59.63,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}這撕心裂肺的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:04.33,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}響徹在宇宙彼岸的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.67,0:23:07.56,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}是那稚拙的鎮魂之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.33,0:23:11.71,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:14.80,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}依然從飄乎的現實中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.28,0:23:17.15,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}找尋你的印記
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:20.75,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}相逢的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.89,0:23:24.48,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}消散的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:28.73,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我都歷歷在目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.00,0:23:31.77,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}因為曾經深愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:35.53,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}萌生的情愫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.73,0:23:39.30,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}殘留的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:43.45,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我都銘記在心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.78,0:23:50.38,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}一路前行
Comment: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:19.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,=============STORY===============
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.86,0:00:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可真是不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我可不是在跟你說笑話啊 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.13,0:00:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.77,0:00:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.60,0:00:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你比計劃的要慢 所以我一直很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.25,0:00:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 有人來電了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 那我先掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再見 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長 長道 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.57,0:00:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天能讓我住一晚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.15,0:00:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.16,0:00:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒——？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（OP）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:23.91,title,NTP,0,0,0,,啟 動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.70,0:02:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚 晚上好…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 真是得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.99,0:02:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.94,0:02:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從剛才開始就有些奇怪的響動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一個人待著還挺害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.76,0:02:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃點東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗澡的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的管線裡也傳出了奇怪的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 好討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是海苔飯糰…哇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虧你找得到這裡來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 嚇著你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一個人很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到不知道我們還能見幾次面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就覺得難過了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是沒有這種戰爭…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見幾次都不是問題的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們一起打倒奇居子 結束這場戰爭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制裝置已經安裝完成了 科戶瀨博士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了 奴美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次承蒙你幫了大忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫到您是我的榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到她對落合的奇居子學有這麼深的理解…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由蕾博士 那個新武器好像完成了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒有最終完成 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然算是成形了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是用胞衣模擬出的部分還難以控制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以現在的狀態進行啟動試驗會有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要花多久才能做到萬無一失？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估計需要半年時間反覆進行模擬試驗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個武器是與大眾合船交戰所必不可少的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啟動試驗按計劃進行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始進行十七式繼衛改與十八式的混合掌位訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四機掌位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這加速不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有繼衛改參與的四機掌位速度很快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新型推進引擎也穩定下來了 看上去運作得挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是紬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然來遲了 不過我也參加訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是紬的新操縱士 岐神海蘊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:02.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這速度也太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全追不上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底什麼飛行原理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？我 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是也能用在衛人上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岐神 該不會其實你已經弄清楚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾 不明白的地方還多得是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛人隊 現在開始進行與融合個體紬的掌位訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌位解除
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷風先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 要開始了 紬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷風先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好強的機動性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:08:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 谷風和那個融合個體真是默契到家了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 莎瑪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷風機-紬混合掌位的平均速度超過了十八式正常值的8倍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且還有加速空間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旋轉性能值也達到了10倍以上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到竟然這麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛人整備班第5班…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷風長道先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬好像真的很喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們今後也好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 紬就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.96,0:08:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.92,0:09:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀 谷風 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我又有事想拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:37.01,eyecatch,NTP,1023,0,0,,希德尼婭百景　計劃修繕的管線
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,eyecatch,,0,0,0,,(Part-b)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:39.93,eyecatch,NTP,1000,0,0,,希德尼婭百景　新第７號機庫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的管線圖有用嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 託福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是有別的事想拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在找舊管線比較多的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那不是挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你這麼喜歡管線啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我事先調查了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能把這間給我看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 就是外周壁的這裡 或者這個區域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好是人少的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外周壁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.81,*Default,NTP,100,0,0,,{\an7\p1\1a&H8F&\c&HCDCDCD&\pos(16,12)}m 0 0 l 650 0 l 650 450 l 0 450
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.81,*Default,NTP,100,0,0,,{\an7\p1\1a&HFF&\c&HCDCDCD&\pos(16,12)}m 0 0 l 650 0 l 650 64 l 0 64
