Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.81,*Default,NTP,100,0,0,,{\an7\p1\1a&HFF&\c&HCDCDCD&\pos(16,12)}m 172 130 l 172 234 l 650 234 l 650 130
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.81,*Default,NTP,100,0,0,,{\an7\p1\1a&HFF&\c&HCDCDCD&\pos(16,12)}m 0 0 l 650 0 l 650 234 l 0 234
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.81,*Default,NTP,170,0,0,,{\an7\fs60}無限制居住許可證
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.81,*Default,NTP,340,0,0,,{\an7\fs60}谷風長道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.81,*Default,NTP,200,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}希德尼婭軍衛人隊西4管轄區\N下屬高級操縱士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}茲證明以上人物破例獲准居住於\N包括外周壁居住特別區內的區域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.81,*Default,NTP,300,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}出航紀元1010年4月\N希德尼婭軍總司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…無限制居住許可證！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.18,0:10:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是第一次帶人去看外周壁的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要再找找配線圖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過真羨慕你啊 居然能住在外周壁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:10:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操縱士們都必須住在幹線軌道機關附近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這裡怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是老房子了 不過有這麼多舊管線繞來繞去的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…這樣好像有點不太好鑽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有更靠東一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這間怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 這裡好像不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是纈啊 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近休假經常報銷 都抽不出時間來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔你有進到什麼好貨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這難不成是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引力子放射線發射裝置啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理論上最強的武器…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 是自製的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小時候在「架空武器大全」裡見過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「這種武器無堅不摧！」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那本書我到現在都還留著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過話說回來 還真是好懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能喜歡真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷風？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天還讓你陪我直接過去看 真是太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡 能看到漂亮的管線我也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡是住房管理局…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘖 大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回得挺早嘛 還好把鑰匙給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是願意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要直接住下…嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,配線圖？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我今天去看了看要搬過去的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？啊 是 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就是我今天看的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是紬的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 這可是外周壁的房子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要也一起搬過去？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 前提是你願意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 什麼叫前提是我願意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:13:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡可是外周壁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能是能搞到批准
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是像我這樣的普通操縱士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不能住這種地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…沒 沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面寫著允許找一個人同住的…你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 伊札那？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本來是想先跟你商量的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是今天突然有空了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是無所謂 跟你一起搬過去也行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這離車站也太遠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 建築後面就有通往軍事區的升降軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個好地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫紬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那 先屏住氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬說管線裡灰塵很多 所以她準備加個壓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正本來也準備要打掃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了灰塵之外沒什麼問題了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:15:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 都沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:16:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面也很寬敞 來這裡的路上挺舒適的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷風先生 你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去沒什麼精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬…你還沒睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我其實不睡也沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然想睡也能睡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是個怪胎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠貼在後面的牆上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這不是鍬形蟲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噓 你聲音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那大概已經睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我可以摸摸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:16:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過要輕點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是第一次見到活的鍬形蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長得好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我本來就打算放了牠的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於鍬形蟲來說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們肯定只是無法交流的可怕的捕食者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 或許是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許只是彼此太過不同 不知道該怎樣正確地交流而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.55,0:17:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星白…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 谷風先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都這麼晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:17:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再見了 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
