Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.25,0:18:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浮游小行星正通過本艦附近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距離18萬千單位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:19:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得路過 卻不去開採資源啊
